<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
</head>
<body>
<ul>
	<p>
		Your friend found this interesting and wants you to check it out.
	</p>
	<p>
		$ctx.customerNotificationData.currentUserName has suggested you the following link:
	</p>
    <p>
        <a href="$ctx.customerNotificationData.url">$ctx.customerNotificationData.name</a>
    </p>
    <p>
    	<img src="$ctx.customerNotificationData.mediaUrl">
    </p>
    <p>
    	Product Price : R$ctx.customerNotificationData.productPrice
    <p>
        In case the above link doesn't work, please copy and paste the following url in the address bar of your browser 
    </p>
    <p>
        $ctx.customerNotificationData.url
    </p>
    <p>
        $ctx.customerNotificationData.message
    </p>
    <p>
        ${ctx.customerNotificationData.site}.com
    </p>
</ul>
</body>
</html>